comment: Super fun movement! love the tricky, balancey sequence up top.
Fun movement, nice pockets, good flow.
Felt very hard to me, but super cool, intricate sequence.
So fun!! Always nice to have a really classic crimp line.
Super cool movement! Really thought provoking.

Definitely not 5.11. The bottom section felt about the same difficulty as the yellow 5.12b from the same set. One star because this route is dangerous. The clipping stances for lower clips are really bad/ not there, especially since the feet are so bad for the third clip. Because this thing is so sandbagged, it seems really likely that someone who climbs .11a/.11b is going to get on it and deck trying to clip the second or third draw. Top section was really fun--cool movement, felt 5.11a or b depending on your reach.
I don't think it's the beta...but easiest as a dyno!
